content.value:
This day in history, 1799, George Washington dies

A slave owner from age 11, he & his wife eventually came to own over 300 human beings. He never freed a single one in his lifetime

Also, his famous dentures were teeth pulled out of slaves’ heads. He paid 1/3 the going rate
